PrecisAuthority to sign an EXCHANGE OF NOTES constituting an AMENDMENT to the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Kingdom of the Netherlands on Mutual Administrative Assistance in Customs Matters, providing for the extension of the territorial jurisdiction of the Netherlands to include the Netherlands Antilles and Aruba. Provision for this territorial extension by Exchange of Notes is found in Article 22 of the Agreement.
